text: Claes Turitz (28 August 1928 – 1 April 2005) was a Swedish sailor who competed in the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Swedish male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Sweden Category:Sailors at the 1960 Summer Olympics – 5.5 Metre
